{"tid":1737414,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"流水抗爭？留守抗爭？","createTime":"2019-11-19T03:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T09:13:22.000Z","uid":22796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"27af69a4a473cbeb9f0e0d4991866d3b1558d0cd","tid":1737414,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:03:47.000Z","msg":"經過幾次大學戰之後 迴響最大嘅係中大同理大 點解？<br />\n因為呢兩次都係陣地戰 損傷最慘重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇俾曱甴咬都五勞七傷<br />\n重點係 呢兩戰之後 連登分化撚出晒嚟<br />\n<br />\n反觀之前嘅流水式抗爭：裝修 唱歌 黎明<br />\n損傷係最少<br />\n<br />\n要諗吓 留守喺一個地方係正確<br />\n又或者 守喺方個地方先正確<br />\n<br />\n最後請記住大原則<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化 不割席 不篤灰</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9c7f01941b2551d974c94954b3e4c3e907e4f89","tid":1737414,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e812e753931022cefe3a2b27995b52be6458a18","tid":1737414,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9c7f01941b2551d974c94954b3e4c3e907e4f89","tid":1737414,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c26894ab35eab9937dfa88a5f317b9a6d2844b","tid":1737414,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c591a6b317e92a7fc3e5906bab02245eba7f4a69","tid":1737414,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9c7f01941b2551d974c94954b3e4c3e907e4f89","tid":1737414,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma